      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get what you're saying but it feels like a lot of precautions for just a tiny bit of wine. honestly, if i'm just having one glass and then taking the pill, wouldn't that actually help the diazepam work more effectively since they both help with relaxation? it seems like it would just make the transition to sleep smoother rather than being a huge risk.",
